      "Title": "WAYN.Games.Blob.BlobHashMapBuilder<TKey, TValue>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/WAYN.Games.Blob.BlobHashMapBuilder-2.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Fluent builder for constructing a <xref href=\"WAYN.Games.Blob.BlobMultiHashMap%602\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> stored in a blob asset.\nAccumulates key-value pairs, automatically rehashes when the load factor is exceeded,\nand produces an immutable BlobAssetReference&lt;T&gt; via <xref href=\"WAYN.Games.Blob.BlobHashMapBuilder%602.CreateBlobAssetReference(Allocator)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
