      "Title": "WAYN.Games.Blob.BlobMultiHashMap<TKey, TValue>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/WAYN.Games.Blob.BlobMultiHashMap-2.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An immutable multi-value hash map stored in a BlobAssetReference&lt;T&gt;.\nSupports multiple values per key with O(1) average bucket lookup and binary search within buckets.\nBuilt using <xref href=\"WAYN.Games.Blob.BlobHashMapBuilder%602\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and intended for read-only access at runtime.</p>\n"
